---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro'
import BackgroundSection from '../components/BackgroundSection.astro'
---

<Layout title="Behind the Scenes | Brianna Marie Rickey">
  <main>
    <BackgroundSection
      backgroundImage="/backgrounds/bts-background.jpg"
      opacity={0.6}
      textOutline={true}
    >
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Behind the Scenes</h1>

      <p class="text-lg mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        This portfolio wasn’t just built—it was carefully crafted with intention, iteration, and a
        whole lot of trial and error.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 mt-10">Elevator Pitch</h2>
      <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-8">
        This is a fully responsive cybersecurity portfolio website built in VSCode using Astro,
        React, and Tailwind CSS. It showcases my skills and projects through an intuitive design
        with dynamic views and easy navigation optimized for both mobile and desktop. The site
        focuses on clean, maintainable code, leveraging AI tools to speed up development while
        ensuring I deeply understand and control every part of the project.
      </p>

      <section class="overflow-x-auto mt-12">
        <table class="min-w-full border border-black text-left text-sm text-white">
          <thead class="bg-black text-white font-semibold">
            <tr>
              <th class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Phase</th>
              <th class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Key Actions & Decisions</th>
              <th class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Outcome</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody class="bg-black">
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">1. Project Bootstrapping</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Create Astro project, minimal cleanup, remove <code>README.md</code>, init Git</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Clear Astro skeleton structure</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">2. Core Styling</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Install Tailwind, update <code>tailwind.config.cjs</code>, <code
                  >postcss.config.cjs</code
                >, global styles in <code>src/styles/global.css</code></td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Tailwind utilities available project-wide</td
              >
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">3. React Integration</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Install React, <code>@astrojs/react</code></td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Ready to drop in JSX components</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">4. Netlify Adapter</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Install <code>@astrojs/netlify</code>, update config in <code
                  >astro.config.mjs</code
                >, add adapter import</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Auto builds use Netlify-friendly output</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">5. Global Layout</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Created <code>src/layouts/Layout.astro</code> with shared header/footer</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Single shared shell for every page</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">6. Pages</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Home, About, Projects, Behind the Scenes</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Clear, minimal routing</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">7. Components</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Made <code>BackgroundSection.astro</code>, <code>ProjectCard.astro</code>, etc.</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Re-usable chunks per section</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">8. PDFs & Static Assets</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Placed all PDFs in <code>public/projects/</code> and linked in cards</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Downloads open in new tab</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">9. Git & GitHub</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Commits, <code>.gitignore</code>, pushed to GitHub</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Source fully tracked & visible</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">10. Netlify Deployment</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Connected repo → Netlify → auto-deploy from <code>main</code></td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Live site with deploy preview</td>
            </tr>
            <tr>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">11. Post-Launch Polish</td>
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2"
                >Added <code>_redirects</code> file, final <code>astro.config.mjs</code> cleanup</td
              >
              <td class="border border-black px-4 py-2">Production-ready polish</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </section>

      <div class="text-center mt-12">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-block bg-blue-600 text-white px-6 py-3 rounded hover:bg-blue-700 transition"
        >
          Back to Home
        </a>
      </div>
    </BackgroundSection>
  </main>
</Layout>
